  <h2>
    <span class="">以下豆列推荐</span>
      &nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;&middot;
      <span class="pl">&nbsp;(
          <a href="https://book.douban.com/subject/1351452/doulists">全部</a>
        ) </span>

  </h2>


    <div id="db-doulist-section" class="indent">
      <ul class="bs">
          <li class=""><a class="" href="https://www.douban.com/doulist/648040/" target="_blank">有錢買不到.</a>
                <span class="pl">(知常)</span>
            </li>
          <li class=""><a class="" href="https://www.douban.com/doulist/402929/" target="_blank">书名由三个词语组成</a>
                <span class="pl">(王荣欣)</span>
            </li>
          <li class=""><a class="" href="https://www.douban.com/doulist/1280971/" target="_blank">Nationalism &amp; National Identity</a>
